Gooning Simulator

Just a simple game made with raylib and C.

How to compile?
- Linux (recommended)
    1. Build raylib https://github.com/raysan5/raylib/wiki/Working-on-GNU-Linux
    2. git clone https://github.com/rajeevtapadia/gooning-simulator.git
    3. cd gooning-simulator
    4. make run
    5. enjoy!!

- Windows
    If someone can find a reliable way to build on windows, PR will be 
    appreciated.

- Vibe coder
    The release tab has statically linked binaries for you.


